Package com.intellij.ui.jcef

Class JBCefClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.ui.jcef.JBCefClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Disposable, JBCefDisposable

    public class JBCefClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements JBCefDisposable
    A wrapper over CefClient.

    Provides facilities to add multiple handlers of the same type (CefClient doesn't). All the handlers of the same type are called in the "last-added-last-called" order. When a return value is expected, the last handler's return value is returned as the result. When a CEF callback is passed to the handler, it's the responsibility of the client to manage the callback calls in case when multiple handlers are added.
